'''Marion Bauman''' is a former [[East Germany|East German]] [[Whitewater slalom|slalom canoeist]] who competed in the 1970s. She won two medals in the K-1 team event with a silver in [[1975 ICF Canoe Slalom World Championships|1975]] and a bronze in [[1973 ICF Canoe Slalom World Championships|1973]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Overview of athlete's results|website=CanoeSlalom.net |url=http://www.canoeslalom.net/int/index/index_66.html#2610 |accessdate=30 April 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120503005006/http://www.canoeslalom.net/int/index/index_66.html#2610 |archivedate=3 May 2012 |df= }}</ref>

